-- Abu Dhabi's FGB hires former NBAD banker to lead corp fin advisory services
-- By Stanley Carvalho
-- Tue Aug 19, 2014 06:43AM EDT
-- None



ABU DHABI, Aug 19 (Reuters) - Major Abu Dhabi lender First Gulf Bank <FGB.AD> has hired a former banker at National Bank of Abu Dhabi <NBAD.AD> as head of its corporate finance advisory services, FGB said on Tuesday.

Michael Aissaoui will oversee expansion of the bank's advisory activities for clients regionally and globally. In April Reuters reported that Aissaoui and another senior banker, Nicholas Gilani, were leaving NBAD to pursue other opportunities. [ID:nL6N0NL39F]